# Cloudflare Pages routing rules.
#
# This Pages project serves only the rhymegold.com domain (lyricgenie.app
# is on a separate GitHub Pages deploy), so we can safely rewrite the
# deployment root to the RhymeGold-branded shell at /rhymegold/index.html
# without affecting any other site. Status 200 = rewrite (URL bar stays
# as rhymegold.com), not a redirect.
#
# All other paths (assets, fonts, JS) have no rule and pass through to
# their actual locations under public/ — no further rewriting needed.
/                /rhymegold/index.html  200
/index.html      /rhymegold/index.html  200
